            , and live in Britannia-gardens, Hoxton. On the 22d of December, about half-past six o'clock, I was crossing the road with my <rs id="t18240114-147-viclabel832" type="occupation">mother</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240114-147-victim1287 t18240114-147-viclabel832"></join>'s shawl on, and when I was half way across, somebody took it off my back. I turned round, and saw a man run down the street - I called Stop thief! and he was taken, but I had lost sight of him. I saw the shawl picked up in the street he ran down. I cannot speak to the man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18240114-147-person1292">
                  CHARLES 
                  CONSTABLE
               <interp inst="t18240114-147-person1292" type="surname" value="CONSTABLE"></interp>
