                     <interp inst="t18240114-147-person1292" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prisoner take the shawl off this girl's back. I was two or three yards behind him, and perceived him put it under his coat - he ran about one hundred yards, and I took him. An officer came up. I got a lantern and found it. I had not seen him drop it.</p>

               <p>ELEAZER HECK. I am this girl's father-in-law. The shawl is mine.</p>
               <p>
            
